quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  75,20,"Ala woni ko hoɗon njiɗi aduna jaawɗo o ko gasata."
  75,21,"Ngaccon La'akara."
  75,22,"Je'ece malaaɓe ñande heen na fooyni."
  75,23,"Hoɗe ndaara fa'ade e joom mu' en."
  75,24,"E je'ece ñirɓaniiɗe ñande heen."
  75,25,"Hoɗe cikka ma telline e mu' en musiiba mawɗo."
  75,26,"Ala sindu yottiima bororde."
  75,27,"Wi'e hombo woni moccaoowa."
  75,28,"O yananee ko ɗum ceergal e aduna."
  75,29,"Korlal ngal fiilto e korlal."
  75,30,"Ko ta joom ma ñande heen woni ruttorde."
  75,31,"O gooŋɗinaani o juulaani."
  75,32,"Kono o yeddu o ɗuurnii."
  75,33,"Refti o yahi to koreeji makko hombo wasoo."
  75,34,"Halkaare woodaniima e halkaare."
  75,35,"Refti halkaare kadi woodanii ma e halkaare titi."
  75,36,"Mbele aade o sikku o accete hombo duda."
  75,37,"Mbele o wonaana toɓɓe maniyyu juppateende e rannga."
  75,38,"Refti o wonti heɗɗere o tagi o fonndi."
  75,39,"O waɗI heen kuɓe ɗiɗi dewel e gorel."
  75,40,"Mbele oon hattanaani wuurtin'de maayɓe."
  76,1,"Mbele arii e aade tumo e yonta nde o wonaana hay hu'unde jaŋtateende."
  76,2,"Min tagii aade e toɓɓere jillunde ndiyam gorko e debbo min kumpitoo mbo min laatini mbo nanoowo ji'oowo."
  76,3,"Miin peewnii mbo e laawol o yetta wollo o yedda."
  76,4,"Pellet Miin keblinii he'eferɓe callalle e tonngi e yiite."
  76,5,"Pellet ɗigguɓe ɓe na njara e kaas jilluɗo kaafuur."